{
  "1": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Then Bildad, from the Shuah area, spoke to Job. He said,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "2": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\"Job, how much longer will you talk like this?\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "What you say is as useless as a big wind.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "3": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Almighty God certainly never does anything unfairly.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "He always does what is right.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "4": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Your children have sinned against him;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "this is evident because he has punished them for those evil things.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "5": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "But now, if only you will earnestly request Almighty God to help you!\n\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "6": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "If only you were pure and honest!\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Then he will surely do something good for you\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and reward you by giving your family back to you and making you prosper.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "7": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Even though you were not very prosperous before,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "during the last stage of your life you would become very wealthy.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "8": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "I request you to think about what happened long ago\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and to consider what our ancestors found out.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "9": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "It seems as though we were born only yesterday\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and we know very little;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "our time here on the earth disappears quickly, like a shadow that is here and then gone.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "10": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "So why not allow your ancestors to teach you anything?\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Let them tell you what they learned!\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "11": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Papyrus certainly does not grow away from marshland;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "reeds certainly cannot grow where there is no water.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "12": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "If the water dries up while they are blossoming,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "they wither more quickly than any other plant.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "13": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Those who do not pay attention to what God says are like those reeds;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "godless people stop confidently expecting that good things will happen to them.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "14": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The things they confidently expect to happen do not happen;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "things they trust will help them are as weak as a spider's web.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "15": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "If they think they will be safe because they are wealthy, they will not be safe;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "the things they think will keep them safeâ€”those things will disappear.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "16": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Godless people are like plants that are watered before the sun rises:\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "their shoots spread all over the gardens.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "17": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The roots of those plants twist around the piles of stones\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and cling tightly to the rocks.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "18": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "But if a gardener pulls those plants out,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "it is as though the place where they were planted says, 'They were never here!'\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "That is what happens to wicked people who do not pay attention to what God says.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "19": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Truly, this is all the joy that evil people have:\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "other people just come and take their places.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "20": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "So, I tell you, Job, God will not reject you if you honor him,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "but he does not help evil people.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "21": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "He will always enable you to laugh\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and to\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "shout joyfully.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "22": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "But those who hate you will be very ashamed,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and the homes of wicked people will disappear.\"\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      }
    ]
  },
  "front": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "p",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "paragraph"
      }
    ]
  }
}